== Examples
=== Left-Hand Riemann sum

```example
riesketcher(
    x => calc.pow(x, 3) + 4,
    method: "left",
    start: -3.1,
    end: 3.5,
    n: 10,
    plot-x-tick-step: 1,
)
```

=== Midpoint Riemann sum

```example
riesketcher(
    x => -calc.pow(x, 2) + 9,
    method: "mid",
    domain: (-4, 4),
    start: -3,
    end: 3,
    n: 6,
    plot-x-tick-step: 1,
)
```
=== Right-method Riemann sum

```example
riesketcher(
    x => 16 - x * x,
    method: "right",
    end: 6,
    n: 6,
    domain: (-1, auto),
    plot-x-tick-step: 1,
)
```

